{"chapter_number":79,"bismillah_pre":true,"revelation_order":81,"revelation_place":"makkah","name_arabic":"النازعات","name_complex":"An-Nāzi`āt","name_simple":"An-Nazi'at","verses_count":46,"pages":[583,584],"meaning":{"text":"Those who drag forth","en":"Those who drag forth","id":"Malaikat yang Mencabut"},"verses":[[[1,5713,"79:1","وَالنَّازِعَاتِ غَرْقًا",["I swear by the angels who violently pull out the souls of the wicked,","Demi (malaikat) yang mencabut (nyawa) dengan keras."],583,30,59,233,null,null],[2,5714,"79:2","وَالنَّاشِطَاتِ نَشْطًا",["And by those who gently draw out the souls of the blessed,","Demi (malaikat) yang mencabut (nyawa) dengan lemah lembut."],583,30,59,233,null,null],[3,5715,"79:3","وَالسَّابِحَاتِ سَبْحًا",["And by those who float in space,","Demi (malaikat) yang turun dari langit dengan cepat,"],583,30,59,233,null,null],[4,5716,"79:4","فَالسَّابِقَاتِ سَبْقًا",["Then those who are foremost going ahead,","dan (malaikat) yang mendahului dengan kencang,"],583,30,59,233,null,null],[5,5717,"79:5","فَالْمُدَبِّرَاتِ أَمْرًا",["Then those who regulate the affair.","dan (malaikat) yang mengatur urusan (dunia)."],583,30,59,233,null,null],[6,5718,"79:6","يَوْمَ تَرْجُفُ الرَّاجِفَةُ",["The day on which the quaking one shall quake,","(Sungguh, kamu akan dibangkitkan) pada hari ketika tiupan pertama mengguncangkan alam,"],583,30,59,233,null,null],[7,5719,"79:7","تَتْبَعُهَا الرَّادِفَةُ",["What must happen afterwards shall follow it.","(tiupan pertama) itu diiringi oleh tiupan kedua."],583,30,59,233,null,null],[8,5720,"79:8","قُلُوبٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ وَاجِفَةٌ",["Hearts on that day shall palpitate,","Hati manusia pada waktu itu merasa sangat takut,"],583,30,59,233,null,null],[9,5721,"79:9","أَبْصَارُهَا خَاشِعَةٌ",["Their eyes cast down.","pandangannya tunduk."],583,30,59,233,null,null],[10,5722,"79:10","يَقُولُونَ أَإِنَّا لَمَرْدُودُونَ فِي الْحَافِرَةِ",["They say: Shall we indeed be restored to (our) first state?","(Orang-orang kafir) berkata, “Apakah kita benar-benar akan dikembalikan kepada kehidupan yang semula?"],583,30,59,233,null,null],[11,5723,"79:11","أَإِذَا كُنَّا عِظَامًا نَّخِرَةً",["What! when we are rotten bones?","Apakah (akan dibangkitkan juga) apabila kita telah menjadi tulang belulang yang hancur?”"],583,30,59,233,null,null],[12,5724,"79:12","قَالُوا تِلْكَ إِذًا كَرَّةٌ خَاسِرَةٌ",["They said: That then would be a return occasioning loss.","Mereka berkata, “Kalau demikian, itu adalah suatu pengembalian yang merugikan.”"],583,30,59,233,null,null],[13,5725,"79:13","فَإِنَّمَا هِيَ زَجْرَةٌ وَاحِدَةٌ",["But it shall be only a single cry,","Maka pengembalian itu hanyalah dengan sekali tiupan saja."],583,30,59,233,null,null],[14,5726,"79:14","فَإِذَا هُم بِالسَّاهِرَةِ",["When lo! they shall be wakeful.","Maka seketika itu mereka hidup kembali di bumi (yang baru)."],583,30,59,233,null,null],[15,5727,"79:15","هَلْ أَتَاكَ حَدِيثُ مُوسَىٰ",["Has not there come to you the story of Musa?","Sudahkah sampai kepadamu (Muhammad) kisah Musa?"],583,30,59,233,null,null],[16,5728,"79:16","إِذْ نَادَاهُ رَبُّهُ بِالْوَادِ الْمُقَدَّسِ طُوًى",["When his Lord called upon him in the holy valley, twice,","Ketika Tuhan memanggilnya (Musa) di lembah suci yaitu Lembah Tuwa;"],584,30,59,233,null,null],[17,5729,"79:17","اذْهَبْ إِلَىٰ فِرْعَوْنَ إِنَّهُ طَغَىٰ",["Go to Firon, surely he has become inordinate.","pergilah engkau kepada Fir‘aun! Sesungguhnya dia telah melampaui batas,"],584,30,59,233,null,null],[18,5730,"79:18","فَقُلْ هَل لَّكَ إِلَىٰ أَن تَزَكَّىٰ",["Then say: Have you (a desire) to purify yourself:","Maka katakanlah (kepada Fir‘aun), “Adakah keinginanmu untuk membersihkan diri (dari kesesatan),"],584,30,59,233,null,null],[19,5731,"79:19","وَأَهْدِيَكَ إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ فَتَخْشَىٰ",["And I will guide you to your Lord so that you should fear.","dan engkau akan kupimpin ke jalan Tuhanmu agar engkau takut kepada-Nya?”"],584,30,59,233,null,null],[20,5732,"79:20","فَأَرَاهُ الْآيَةَ الْكُبْرَىٰ",["So he showed him the mighty sign.","Lalu (Musa) memperlihatkan kepadanya mukjizat yang besar."],584,30,59,233,null,null],[21,5733,"79:21","فَكَذَّبَ وَعَصَىٰ",["But he rejected (the truth) and disobeyed.","Tetapi dia (Fir‘aun) mendustakan dan mendurhakai."],584,30,59,233,null,null],[22,5734,"79:22","ثُمَّ أَدْبَرَ يَسْعَىٰ",["Then he went back hastily.","Kemudian dia berpaling seraya berusaha menantang (Musa)."],584,30,59,233,null,null],[23,5735,"79:23","فَحَشَرَ فَنَادَىٰ",["Then he gathered (men) and called out.","Kemudian dia mengumpulkan (pembesar-pembesarnya) lalu berseru (memanggil kaumnya)."],584,30,59,233,null,null],[24,5736,"79:24","فَقَالَ أَنَا رَبُّكُمُ الْأَعْلَىٰ",["Then he said: I am your lord, the most high.","(Seraya) berkata, “Akulah tuhanmu yang paling tinggi.”"],584,30,59,233,null,null],[25,5737,"79:25","فَأَخَذَهُ اللَّهُ نَكَالَ الْآخِرَةِ وَالْأُولَىٰ",["So Allah seized him with the punishment of the hereafter and the former life.","Maka Allah menghukumnya dengan azab di akhirat dan siksaan di dunia."],584,30,59,233,null,null],[26,5738,"79:26","إِنَّ فِي ذَٰلِكَ لَعِبْرَةً لِّمَن يَخْشَىٰ",["Most surely there is in this a lesson to him who fears.","Sungguh, pada yang demikian itu terdapat pelajaran bagi orang yang takut (kepada Allah)."],584,30,59,233,null,null],[27,5739,"79:27","أَأَنتُمْ أَشَدُّ خَلْقًا أَمِ السَّمَاءُ ۚ بَنَاهَا",["Are you the harder to create or the heaven? He made it.","Apakah penciptaan kamu yang lebih hebat ataukah langit yang telah dibangun-Nya?"],584,30,59,233,null,null],[28,5740,"79:28","رَفَعَ سَمْكَهَا فَسَوَّاهَا",["He raised high its height, then put it into a right good state.","Dia telah meninggikan bangunannya lalu menyempurnakannya,"],584,30,59,233,null,null],[29,5741,"79:29","وَأَغْطَشَ لَيْلَهَا وَأَخْرَجَ ضُحَاهَا",["And He made dark its night and brought out its light.","dan Dia menjadikan malamnya (gelap gulita), dan menjadikan siangnya (terang benderang)."],584,30,59,233,null,null],[30,5742,"79:30","وَالْأَرْضَ بَعْدَ ذَٰلِكَ دَحَاهَا",["And the earth, He expanded it after that.","Dan setelah itu bumi Dia hamparkan."],584,30,59,233,null,null],[31,5743,"79:31","أَخْرَجَ مِنْهَا مَاءَهَا وَمَرْعَاهَا",["He brought forth from it its water and its pasturage.","Darinya Dia pancarkan mata air, dan (ditumbuhkan) tumbuh-tumbuhannya."],584,30,59,233,null,null],[32,5744,"79:32","وَالْجِبَالَ أَرْسَاهَا",["And the mountains, He made them firm,","Dan gunung-gunung Dia pancangkan dengan teguh."],584,30,59,233,null,null],[33,5745,"79:33","مَتَاعًا لَّكُمْ وَلِأَنْعَامِكُمْ",["A provision for you and for your cattle.","(Semua itu) untuk kesenanganmu dan untuk hewan-hewan ternakmu."],584,30,59,233,null,null],[34,5746,"79:34","فَإِذَا جَاءَتِ الطَّامَّةُ الْكُبْرَىٰ",["But when the great predominating calamity comes;","Maka apabila malapetaka besar (hari Kiamat) telah datang,"],584,30,59,233,null,null],[35,5747,"79:35","يَوْمَ يَتَذَكَّرُ الْإِنسَانُ مَا سَعَىٰ",["The day on which man shall recollect what he strove after,","yaitu pada hari (ketika) manusia teringat akan apa yang telah dikerjakannya,"],584,30,59,233,null,null],[36,5748,"79:36","وَبُرِّزَتِ الْجَحِيمُ لِمَن يَرَىٰ",["And the hell shall be made manifest to him who sees","dan neraka diperlihatkan dengan jelas kepada setiap orang yang melihat."],584,30,59,233,null,null],[37,5749,"79:37","فَأَمَّا مَن طَغَىٰ",["Then as for him who is inordinate,","Maka adapun orang yang melampaui batas,"],584,30,59,233,null,null],[38,5750,"79:38","وَآثَرَ الْحَيَاةَ الدُّنْيَا",["And prefers the life of this world,","dan lebih mengutamakan kehidupan dunia,"],584,30,59,233,null,null],[39,5751,"79:39","فَإِنَّ الْجَحِيمَ هِيَ الْمَأْوَىٰ",["Then surely the hell, that is the abode.","maka sungguh, nerakalah tempat tinggalnya."],584,30,59,233,null,null],[40,5752,"79:40","وَأَمَّا مَنْ خَافَ مَقَامَ رَبِّهِ وَنَهَى النَّفْسَ عَنِ الْهَوَىٰ",["And as for him who fears to stand in the presence of his Lord and forbids the soul from low desires,","Dan adapun orang-orang yang takut kepada kebesaran Tuhannya dan menahan diri dari (keinginan) hawa nafsunya,"],584,30,59,233,null,null],[41,5753,"79:41","فَإِنَّ الْجَنَّةَ هِيَ الْمَأْوَىٰ",["Then surely the garden-- that is the abode.","maka sungguh, surgalah tempat tinggal(nya)."],584,30,59,233,null,null],[42,5754,"79:42","يَسْأَلُونَكَ عَنِ السَّاعَةِ أَيَّانَ مُرْسَاهَا",["They ask you about the hour, when it will come.","Mereka (orang-orang kafir) bertanya kepadamu (Muhammad) tentang hari Kiamat, “Kapankah terjadinya?”"],584,30,59,233,null,null],[43,5755,"79:43","فِيمَ أَنتَ مِن ذِكْرَاهَا",["About what! You are one to remind of it.","Untuk apa engkau perlu menyebutkannya (waktunya)?"],584,30,59,233,null,null],[44,5756,"79:44","إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ مُنتَهَاهَا",["To your Lord is the goal of it.","Kepada Tuhanmulah (dikembalikan) kesudahannya (ketentuan waktunya)."],584,30,59,233,null,null],[45,5757,"79:45","إِنَّمَا أَنتَ مُنذِرُ مَن يَخْشَاهَا",["You are only a warner to him who would fear it.","Engkau (Muhammad) hanyalah pemberi peringatan bagi siapa yang takut kepadanya (hari Kiamat)."],584,30,59,233,null,null],[46,5758,"79:46","كَأَنَّهُمْ يَوْمَ يَرَوْنَهَا لَمْ يَلْبَثُوا إِلَّا عَشِيَّةً أَوْ ضُحَاهَا",["On the day that they see it, it will be as though they had not tarried but the latter part of a day or the early part of it.","Pada hari ketika mereka melihat hari Kiamat itu (karena suasananya hebat), mereka merasa seakan-akan hanya (sebentar saja) tinggal (di dunia) pada waktu sore atau pagi hari."],584,30,59,233,null,null]],[[[1,10,583,"&#xfba2;","word","وَالنَّازِعَاتِ",["By those who extract",""]],[2,10,583,"&#xfba3;","word","غَرْقًا",["violently",""]],[3,10,583,"&#xfba4;","end","ﮤ",[null,null]]],[[1,10,583,"&#xfba5;","word","وَالنَّاشِطَاتِ",["And those who draw out","dan yang mencabut"]],[2,10,583,"&#xfba6;","word","نَشْطًا",["gently","perlahan-lahan"]],[3,10,583,"&#xfba7;","end","ﮧ",[null,null]]],[[1,10,583,"&#xfba8;","word","وَالسَّابِحَاتِ",["And those who glid